1. It requires 2 libraries.

1.1 Libevent, latest version = 2.0.22
https://sourceforge.net/projects/levent/files/libevent/libevent-2.0/libevent-2.0.22-stable.tar.gz
./configure
make
sudo make install
ldconfig

1.2 json parser library, latest version = 1.0.2
https://code.google.com/p/rapidjson/wiki/UserGuide
https://github.com/miloyip/rapidjson

cmake .
make
sudo make install

2. It needs to copy the child process VETHeadless in /usr/bin/ directory.